        "timestamp": "2018-07-30 12:08:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nfrom the description, it allows unmarshaled seamlessly from JSON and YAML files, do you mean the .txt file in this patch is the unmarshaled one? \nI'm not clear about its usage, the JSON/YAML is more readable and user-friendly.",
