        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-07-30 12:15:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nYou unmarshal JSON/Yaml separately into a class that implements AbstractParameterGroup. I haven't added support for that generically in here yet although I would like to soon. For the moment, it is done in whatever application functionality.\n\nIf you're using GSON to parse JSON it workslike this:\n\n        try {\n            // Read the parameters from JSON using Gson\n            final Gson gson = new GsonBuilder().create();\n            myParameterGroupInstance = gson.fromJson(new FileReader(\"/patk/to/json/file.json\"), ImplementationOfParameterGroup.class);\n        } catch (final Exception e) {\n            // Handle exceptions here\n                    }",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
